testcase.name: Ensure that admin user can create a user with all the report access
Ensure that appointment tile displays the SMS remainder sent for the appointment as per the settings
Ensure that appointment tile displays the Email remainder sent for the appointment as per the settings
Ensure that the user is able to create a new branch under a practice
Ensure that the user should be able to update the branch details by clicking on the Edit Details button

Ensure that if Account Number settings is selected as "default Numbering" then the account number is getting generated with first 3 letters of the account holder's surname, followed by an incremental number.
Ensure that if a user tries to create an appointment beyond providers availability then system should throw warning message
Ensure that Admin user can edit the existing users
Ensure that Admin user is able to create new visit types
Ensure that admin user is able to save private rates at practice level for procedures
Ensure that admin user is able to save private rates at practice level for medicines
Ensure that admin user is able to save private rates at practice level for consumables
Ensure that user is able to enable/disable the "CC the practice if statements/invoices are emailed to patients" feature
Ensure that invoices with small balances are written off automatically as per the settings
Ensure that if the checkbox "Show a warning if any of the invoice lines are billed at R 0.00" is ON then the patient should get warning message whenever they try to capture an invoice with 0 amount

Ensure that if "Statements and Invoices - Show treating practice no. of treating provider on statements and invoices" checkbox is ON then, the practice number should be displayed on all the statements and Invoices

Ensure that if "Don’t show the medical aid liable total in the Summary section of the statement" checkbox is ON then,the medical aid liable amount should not be displayed on Statements summary section
